subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Who was the first king of Rajasthan?
question_hi: राजस्थान के पहले राजा कौन थे?
explanation_en: Prithviraj Chauhan was the first king of Rajasthan. He ruled during the 12th century and is famous for his valour in battles.
